This is Perl module vars::declare.

INSTALLATION

vars::declare installation is straightforward. If your CPAN shell is set up,
you should just be able to do

    % cpan vars::declare

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

    % perl Makefile.PL
    % make && make test

Then install it:

    % make install

DOCUMENTATION

vars::declare documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    % perldoc vars::declare

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

